<L>__{exterior yard day}
<A>__{max and henry walk through the crowded prison yard.}
<C>__{max}
<D>__{but here's the good news. we got all this time to do. and time is a medium of exchange. you can buy things with it.}
<C>__{max }
<D>__{knowledge. self respect. forgiveness. and in your case, you can figure out what your dream is.}
<A>__{max takes his arm :}
<C>__{max }
<D>__{your dream is your truth is your destiny.}
<A>__{henry looks at him.}
<C>__{henry}
<D>__{i told you. i'm here by mistake.}
<A>__{max shoots a look back at him.}
<C>__{max}
<D>__{there are no mistakes.}
<A>__{max suddenly glimpses some activity over henry's shoulder.}
<C>__{henry}
<D>__{what?}
<A>__{several convicts are making their way towards them... he pulls henry close, his tone suddenly intense :}
<C>__{max}
<D>__{but you're going to have to fight for that dream, henry.}
<C>__{henry}
<D>__{i am.}
<C>__{max}
<D>__{you're at a crossroads now. there are going to be tests!}
<C>__{henry}
<D>__{what tests?}
<A>__{craack! henry's punched in the side of the head. the inmates grab him, throw him to the ground next to max.}
<C>__{max}
<D>__{this is your moment. whatever you do now defines you. go get em!}
<A>__{henry gets up : charges the inmates, arms swinging, taking several down. he gives it everything he's got. they pile into him, pummeling him. henry just keeps fighting...but it's hopeless. guards rush in. max watches.}
